  sodium: 480 mg
author: HelloFresh
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Central America
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/spicy-peruvian-cauli-and-turkey-bowls-65b16835f8a95d57289927fb
